node.text: E se rimani positivo vedrai spuntare il sole tra le nuvole 💫
Quando passi metti il mondo in pausa ❣
Tu dimmi cosa vedi nella forma delle nuvole 🌤

Now the day bleeds
Into nightfall
And you're not here
To get me through it all
I let my guard down
And then you pulled the rug
I was getting kinda used to being someone you loved
Some eyes touch you more than hands ever could 🌙
